## Cost Allocation Tags Configuration

### Account Strategy

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **Account Strategy** | {{ account_strategy }} |
{%- if account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain-based)' %}
| **Domain** | {{ account_domain }} |
| **Tag Applied** | DOMAIN = {{ account_domain }} |
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Environment-based)' %}
| **Environment** | {{ account_environment }} |
| **Tag Applied** | ENVIRONMENT = {{ account_environment }} |
{%- else %}
| **Domain** | {{ account_domain }} |
| **Environment** | {{ account_environment }} |
| **Tags Applied** | DOMAIN = {{ account_domain }}, ENVIRONMENT = {{ account_environment }} |
{%- endif %}

### Tag Source

Tags are referenced from the shared infrastructure database:
- Database: `{{ shared_database_name | upper }}`
- Schema: `{{ governance_name | upper }}`

{%- if account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain-based)' %}

### Domain-Based Strategy

At the account level, only the **DOMAIN** tag is applied:
- All resources in this account are associated with the **{{ account_domain }}** domain

**Environment tagging** will be applied at the database level when you create data products. Each database can be tagged with its environment (Dev, Test, Prod).

{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Environment-based)' %}

### Environment-Based Strategy

At the account level, only the **ENVIRONMENT** tag is applied:
- All resources in this account are associated with the **{{ account_environment }}** environment

**Domain tagging** will be applied at the database level when you create data products. Each database can be tagged with its domain (Sales, Finance, etc.).

{%- else %}

### Domain + Environment Strategy

At the account level, both tags are applied:
- `DOMAIN = {{ account_domain }}`
- `ENVIRONMENT = {{ account_environment }}`

All resources in this account are fully attributed to both dimensions.

{%- endif %}

### Tagging Warehouses

When creating warehouses, apply the appropriate tag(s):

{%- if account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain-based)' %}
```sql
ALTER WAREHOUSE <warehouse_name> 
  SET TAG {{ shared_database_name }}.{{ governance_name }}.DOMAIN = '{{ account_domain }}';
```
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Environment-based)' %}
```sql
ALTER WAREHOUSE <warehouse_name> 
  SET TAG {{ shared_database_name }}.{{ governance_name }}.ENVIRONMENT = '{{ account_environment }}';
```
{%- else %}
```sql
ALTER WAREHOUSE <warehouse_name> 
  SET TAG {{ shared_database_name }}.{{ governance_name }}.DOMAIN = '{{ account_domain }}';
ALTER WAREHOUSE <warehouse_name> 
  SET TAG {{ shared_database_name }}.{{ governance_name }}.ENVIRONMENT = '{{ account_environment }}';
```
{%- endif %}